<br>
One of the worst things is that this perpetuates the horribly wrong stigma that any black or brown skinned student was admitted <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>due to</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> their ethnicity. It's a stigma that all of those who gained admission by earning it based on merit have to live with.<br>
